╔════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║                    KEY SETUP & STORAGE GUIDE                               ║
║              Venue AI Chat Integration - Supabase + Nvidia API              ║
╚════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

📂 LOCATION OF .env FILE:
   App/backend/.env

⚠️  CRITICAL: Never commit .env to git (already in .gitignore)


═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

1️⃣  SUPABASE KEYS (Training Data Storage)

  Location: Supabase Dashboard → Settings → API

  • SUPABASE_URL
    └─ Find at: Project Settings → API
    └─ Format: https://your-project-id.supabase.co

  • SUPABASE_ANON_KEY (public, safe for frontend)
    └─ Find at: Settings → API → Project API Keys
    └─ Label: "anon public"

  • SUPABASE_SECRET_KEY (private, backend only)
    └─ Find at: Settings → API → Project API Keys
    └─ Label: "service_role secret"


═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

2️⃣  NVIDIA API KEYS (Council of Models)

  Location: https://build.nvidia.com/
  One key per model — or reuse the same key across all three.

  NVIDIA_API_KEY_CREATIVE   → nvidia/llama-3.1-nemotron-70b-instruct (Synthesiser)
  NVIDIA_API_KEY_ANALYTICAL → deepseek/deepseek-v4-pro               (Skeptic)
  NVIDIA_API_KEY_COUNCIL    → qwen/qwen3.5-397b-a17b                  (Local)


═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

📋 COMPLETE .env TEMPLATE

  PG_HOST=your-rds-instance.xxxxxxxxxxxx.ap-south-1.rds.amazonaws.com
  PG_PORT=5432
  PG_DB=polynovea_module2
  PG_USER=your_db_user
  PG_PASSWORD=your_db_password

  # Supabase (Training Data)
  SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-id.supabase.co
  SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_anon_key_here
  SUPABASE_SECRET_KEY=your_secret_key_here

  # Nvidia API Keys (Council of Models)
  NVIDIA_API_KEY_CREATIVE=nvapi-your-key-here
  NVIDIA_MODEL_CREATIVE=nvidia/llama-3.1-nemotron-70b-instruct

  NVIDIA_API_KEY_ANALYTICAL=nvapi-your-key-here
  NVIDIA_MODEL_ANALYTICAL=deepseek/deepseek-v4-pro

  NVIDIA_API_KEY_COUNCIL=nvapi-your-key-here
  NVIDIA_MODEL_COUNCIL=qwen/qwen3.5-397b-a17b


═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

🔐 SECURITY CHECKLIST

  ☐ All keys loaded from .env — never hardcoded in source files
  ☐ .env is in .gitignore — never committed
  ☐ RDS accessible only from EC2 private IP (VPC-only)
  ☐ Rotate keys if any exposure is suspected

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
